  "texts": [
    "It was trained end-to-end using a GCN to provide both more effective and safer personalized recommendations, including a reduction in drug-drug interactions from 7.5 to 3.9% (78).",
    "Net also outperformed baseline models in predicting a patient's current set of treatments (AUC = 0.69) among 1,058 test patients from the MIMIC-III dataset receiving an average of 14 medications.",
    "The detection of ADRs was developed using 12 years of healthcare claims data to create a heterogeneous KG of prescription and disease codes in combination with a GNN.",
    "Proximity-based node embedding was obtained for the drugs and diseases using the Skip-gram model, which also captured temporal sequences.",
    "This was fed to a GNN that leveraged multilayer message passing to predict ADRs (73)."
  ],
